<title>USA: Hilb, Rogal to buy back up to one mln shrs.</title>
<headline>Hilb, Rogal to buy back up to one mln shrs.</headline>
<dateline>RICHMOND, Va. 1997-05-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Hilb, Rogal and Hamilton Co said Tuesday it plans to buy back up to one million additional shares above a previous authorization to repurchase 2.9 million shares.</p>
<p>The latest repurchase program is to take place in the open market or in private transactions.</p>
<p>Since the initial buyback was authorized in November 1990, the company has purchased 2,665,984 shares, it said.</p>
